<dd><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREF.3Cspan_style.3D.22font-variant:small-caps.3B.22.3ESchele.2C_Linda.3C.2Fspan.3Eand_.3Cspan_style.3D.22font-variant:small-caps.3B.22.3E.5B.5BMary_Miller.7CMary_Ellen_Miller.5D.5D.3C.2Fspan.3E1992"><a href="/wiki/Linda_Schele" title="Linda Schele"><span style="font-variant:small-caps;">Schele, Linda</span></a>; and <span style="font-variant:small-caps;"><a href="/wiki/Mary_Miller" title="Mary Miller">Mary Ellen Miller</a></span> (1992). <i>Blood of Kings: Dynasty and Ritual in Maya Art</i>. <a href="/w/index.php?title=Justin_Kerr&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Justin Kerr (page does not exist)">Justin Kerr</a> (photographer) (2nd paperback edn., reprint with corrections ed.). New York: <a href="/wiki/George_Braziller" title="George Braziller">George Braziller</a>. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0807612782" class="internal">ISBN 0-8076-1278-2</a>. <a href="/wiki/Online_Computer_Library_Center" title="Online Computer Library Center">OCLC</a> <a href="http://worldcat.org/oclc/41441466" class="external text" title="http://worldcat.org/oclc/41441466" rel="nofollow">41441466</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Blood+of+Kings%3A+Dynasty+and+Ritual+in+Maya+Art&amp;rft.aulast=%3Cspan+style%3D%22font-variant%3Asmall-caps%3B%22%3ESchele%2C+Linda%3C%2Fspan%3E&amp;rft.au=%3Cspan+style%3D%22font-variant%3Asmall-caps%3B%22%3ESchele%2C+Linda%3C%2Fspan%3E&amp;rft.au=and+%3Cspan+style%3D%22font-variant%3Asmall-caps%3B%22%3E%5B%5BMary+Miller%7CMary+Ellen+Miller%5D%5D%3C%2Fspan%3E&amp;rft.date=1992&amp;rft.edition=2nd+paperback+edn.%2C+reprint+with+corrections&amp;rft.place=New+York&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BGeorge+Braziller%5D%5D&amp;rft_id=info:oclcnum/41441466&amp;rft.isbn=0-8076-1278-2&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Human_sacrifice_in_Aztec_culture"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span>